Nelson McDowell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nelson_McDowell 0 Nelson McDowell (August 14, 1870 – November 3, 1947) was an American actor. He appeared in 176 films between 1917 and 1945. He was born in Greenville, Missouri and died in Hollywood, California after he shot himself. Nelson_McDowell ( August_14_,_1870 – November_3_,_1947 ) was an_American_actor .
